    "English": "A high-powered matter teleportation device, this personal translocator allows any connected Exocraft to be instantly transported to your location, from <span class=\"name name-stellar\">anywhere</span> in the galaxy.<br><br>Interfaces with the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Exosuit Quick Menu</span> for ease of use.",
